milestones.description: This is the highest match aggregate (512) involving teams Australia & Zimbabwe in ODIs
Dave Houghton has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (42) in an innings in ODIs for ZIM, going past Fletcher's 28
Iain Butchart has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Dave Houghton's 1
Iain Butchart has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (4) for ZIM, going past Kevin Curran
Kevin Curran has conceded the most runs in an innings (57) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Peter Rawson's record of 54
Dave Houghton has become the top scorer for ZIM in ODIs with 159 runs, going past Fletcher's 153
Kevin Curran and Dave Houghton's 103-run partnership is ZIM's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 92 between Dave Houghton and Fletcher
Dave Houghton's 84 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for ZIM), surpassing Fletcher's 71
Kevin Curran and Dave Houghton's 103-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 70 between Fletcher and Kevin Curran
John Traicos and Vince Hogg's 27-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 7 between John Traicos and Iain Butchart
